title: New Artist Larry Fleet Blows Us Away + How Jake Owen Discovered Him At A Wedding + Controversial Draft: Best Cartoons + Mailbag: 11 year old daughter wants to be a “Sexy Devil”
itunes:title: New Artist Larry Fleet Blows Us Away + How Jake Owen Discovered Him At A Wedding + Controversial Draft: Best Cartoons + Mailbag: 11 year old daughter wants to be a “Sexy Devil”
description:
New artist Larry Fleets stops by to perform his song “Where I Find God”, talks about how Jake Owen discovered him at a wedding and his new album “Stack of Records”. We draft our favorite cartoons. We help a listener who has a problem with her 11 year old daughter’s Halloween costume...she needs advice on her wanting to be a ‘sexy devil’.
